All references to the "Division of Safety" or its director
shall be deemed to refer to the Office for Local Government or its
commissioner, respectively. See L. 1960, ch. 321. State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
